{"title":"Fox’s New Dropframe Pro Helmet Gains eBike Certification","link":"https://bikerumor.com/fox-dropframe-pro-helmet-gains-ebike-certification/","date":1703017691000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"1121\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-hero.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-hero.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-hero-297x260.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-hero-800x701.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-hero-120x105.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-hero-768x673.jpeg 768w\" /></p>\n<p>Headquartered in Irvine, Califonia, <a href=\"https://www.foxracing.com/\">Fox Racing</a> is a global force in motocross and mountain bike safety equipment and apparel. Today they introduce some updates to their “<a href=\"https://www.foxracing.com/product/dropframe-pro-helmet%C2%A0/31453.html?dwvar_31453_color=053&amp;dwvar_31453_size=S&amp;cgid=helmets-mtb-dropframe-dropframepro\">first to market</a>” Dropframe Pro helmet. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-side-e1703013912762.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"594\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-side-e1703013912762-800x594.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro front side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-side-e1703013912762-800x594.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-side-e1703013912762-297x221.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-side-e1703013912762-120x89.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-side-e1703013912762-768x571.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-side-e1703013912762.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/Fox Racing)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The updates future similar upgrades as the Proframe RS with an all-new aesthetic, as well as a list of features that will further enhance the performance of the classic 3/4 shell silhouette.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Mips-Boa.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Mips-Boa-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro Mips Boa\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Mips-Boa-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Mips-Boa-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Mips-Boa-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Mips-Boa-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Mips-Boa.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-jaw-protection.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-jaw-protection-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro jaw protection\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-jaw-protection-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-jaw-protection-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-jaw-protection-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-jaw-protection-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-jaw-protection.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/fox-first-visor-free-helmet-crossframe-pro-downcountry-gravel/\" target=\"_blank\">Dropframe Pro</a> is an open-face, 3/4 enduro helmet, featuring MIPS and a BOA Fit System. It uses increased ventilation, plus an Ionic anti-microbial liner and cheek pads to optimize fit. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-back-e1703014092108.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-back-e1703014092108-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-back-e1703014092108-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-back-e1703014092108-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-back-e1703014092108-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-back-e1703014092108-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-back-e1703014092108-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-back-e1703014092108.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With its increased coverage for the ears, jaw, and back of the head, FOX says that “this helmet provides the most complete coverage we offer in an open-face helmet”. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Dropframe Pro also elevates safety to another level by meeting the NTA-8776 eBike helmet certification standard. That should give the user a lot more confidence to push the limits while riding.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-front.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-top.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-top-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro top\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-top-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-top-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-top-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-top-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-top.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This new update of the Dropframe Pro brings a few more details that riders will love. Like a new 3-position, adjustable visor, and Big Bore front vents, with a designated area designed for eyewear storage. The vent profile and decreased surface area work together to help with cooling. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-fidlock.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-fidlock-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro fidlock\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-fidlock-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-fidlock-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-fidlock-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-fidlock-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-fidlock.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-dedicated-for-eyewear.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-dedicated-for-eyewear-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro dedicated for eyewear\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-dedicated-for-eyewear-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-dedicated-for-eyewear-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-dedicated-for-eyewear-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-dedicated-for-eyewear-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-dedicated-for-eyewear.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There is also the Fidlock magnetic closure and a removable GoPro mount that fits under the visor. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Dropframe Pro Helmet Retail, Details, and Specs </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $280</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sizes: Small, Medium, and Large (see size chart below)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Colors: Matte Black, Purple, Black/White, Midnight Blue, Black Camouflage, Orange Flame, Olive Green, Oat Brown</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the box: One thin and one thick cheek pad set, one thin and thick headliner, a removable under-visor GoPro mount</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>BOA® Fit System for class-leading fit and security</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Mips added protection system has been proven to reduce the rotational motion when implemented in a helmet by absorbing and redirecting energies and forces otherwise transmitted to the brain</li>\n\n\n\n<li>3-position adjustable visor compatible with goggles</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Removable under visor GoPro mount included</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Big Bore front vents include eyewear storage recess</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Increased ventilation and decreased surface contact area improve cooling</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ionic+® anti-microbial liner and cheek pads to optimize fit</li>\n\n\n\n<li>FIDLOCK magnetic closure</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Meets the NTA-8776 E-bike helmet certification standard</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Dropframe Pro Size Chart</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Size-chart.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"146\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Size-chart-800x146.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro Size chart\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Size-chart-800x146.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Size-chart-297x54.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Size-chart-120x22.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Size-chart-768x140.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Size-chart.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Dropframe Pro Colors</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Midnight-blu.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Midnight-blu-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro Midnight blu\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Midnight-blu-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Midnight-blu-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Midnight-blu-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Midnight-blu-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Midnight-blu.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-and-White.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-and-White-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro Black and White\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-and-White-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-and-White-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-and-White-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-and-White-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-and-White.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camo.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camo-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro Matte Black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camo-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camo-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camo-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camo-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camo.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Orange-Flame.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Orange-Flame-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro Orange Flame\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Orange-Flame-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Orange-Flame-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Orange-Flame-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Orange-Flame-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Orange-Flame.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Purple.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Purple-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro Purple\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Purple-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Purple-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Purple-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Purple-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Purple.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camoflauge.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camoflauge-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"FOX Dropframe Pro Black Camoflauge\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camoflauge-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camoflauge-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camoflauge-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/FOX-Dropframe-Pro-Black-Camoflauge-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp